rows.label: qst650441_msg0001
rows.name:
Ahh, there are friends!
Me search high and low and all
places in between for you!

rows.label: qst650441_msg0002
rows.name:
Please to make acquaintance of
Dokedoke, top-rated courier
service in some places in Alst!

rows.label: qst650441_msg0003
rows.name:
Dokedoke come bearing special
delivery from village of Iyasaki,
sender name of Correl.

rows.label: qst650441_msg0004
rows.name:
Friends curious about contents
of package?

rows.label: qst650441_msg0005
rows.name:
Dokedoke know exactly what
is inside!

rows.label: qst650441_msg0006
rows.name:
"Kukuri fished this pretty-looking
stone up from the Cloud Sea.
We thought you might like it."

rows.label: qst650441_msg0008
rows.name:
Incidentally, is probably worth
to mention "pretty-looking stone"
actually refer to Core Crystal.

rows.label: qst650441_msg0010
rows.name:
Dokedoke did nothing wrong!
Why friends look at me like commit
conduct unbecoming of deliverypon?!

rows.label: qst650441_msg0011
rows.name:
All right, Dokedoke spill beans. Me
thought if delivery was food on verge of
spoilage, would have to gobble up...

rows.label: qst650441_msg0012
rows.name:
But friends are to blame here! Would
not have happened if not wandering
from place to place whole time!

rows.label: qst650441_msg0013
rows.name:
A-anyway...
Friends should be taking Core Crystal.

rows.label: qst650441_msg0014
rows.name: Okay, that take care of that...

rows.label: qst650441_msg0015
rows.name:
Be sure to rate Dokedoke least
four and half stars!
